{"title":"Omnium Tilting Rack Bracket","link":"https://theradavist.com/omnium-tilting-rack-bracket/","date":1727967657000,"content":"<div>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1480\" height=\"986\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554602-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-3-landscape-72dpi-1725c3-original-1727866104.jpg?fit=1200,986&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554602-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-3-landscape-72dpi-1725c3-original-1727866104.jpg?w=1480&amp;quality=75 1480w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554602-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-3-landscape-72dpi-1725c3-original-1727866104.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554602-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-3-landscape-72dpi-1725c3-original-1727866104.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p><em>OMNIUM, makers of <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/omnium-cargo-bike-review/\" target=\"_blank\">cargo bikes that ride like normal bikes</a>, just announced a new <a href=\"https://omniumcargo.com/shop/product/tilting-rack-bracket/\" target=\"_blank\">Tilting Rack Bracket</a>, an innovative accessory designed to further enhance the versatility and storage potential of OMNIUM Cargo and Mini-Max models…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1480\" height=\"986\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554601-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-1-landscape-72dpi-6f795a-original-1727866104.jpg?fit=1200,986&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554601-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-1-landscape-72dpi-6f795a-original-1727866104.jpg?w=1480&amp;quality=75 1480w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554601-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-1-landscape-72dpi-6f795a-original-1727866104.jpg?resize=1200,799&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554601-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-studio-1-landscape-72dpi-6f795a-original-1727866104.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w\" /></p>\n<p>The Tilting Rack Bracket features a quick-release hinge that enables the front cargo rack to tilt effortlessly in seconds, allowing for more compact storage and easy navigation through tight spaces — truly a game-changer. In addition, it includes a quick-release pin for complete rack detachment, for those who need to change their bike’s final form on the go.</p>\n<p>Check out more at <a href=\"https://omniumcargo.com/shop/product/tilting-rack-bracket/\" target=\"_blank\">Omnium</a>!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554583-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-home-3-landscape-72dpi-d59897-original-1727865258.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554583-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-home-3-landscape-72dpi-d59897-original-1727865258.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554583-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-home-3-landscape-72dpi-d59897-original-1727865258.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554583-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-home-3-landscape-72dpi-d59897-original-1727865258.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554583-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-home-3-landscape-72dpi-d59897-original-1727865258.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554583-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-home-3-landscape-72dpi-d59897-original-1727865258.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/554583-omnium_tilting_rack_bracket-home-3-landscape-72dpi-d59897-original-1727865258.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><em>For an ultra-narrow storage solution, pair the Tilting Rack Bracket with a turnable stem and folding/removable pedals. Together, these accessories can reduce the bike’s width to as little as 21cm (excluding an extended kickstand). OMNIUM recommends the BySchulz <u><a href=\"https://byschulz.com/product/stem-twist-sds/?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\">Twist </a></u><u><a href=\"https://byschulz.com/product/stem-twist-sds/?lang=en\" target=\"_blank\">SDS</a></u> stem and MKS <u><a href=\"https://mkspedal.com/?q=en/product/term/9\" target=\"_blank\">Folding</a></u> or <u><a href=\"https://mkspedal.com/?q=en/product/term/4\" target=\"_blank\">Ezy</a></u> quick-release pedals for the ultimate in space-saving efficiency, transforming a Cargo or Mini-Max into one of the slimmest and lightest cargo bikes on the market — even narrower than a road bike.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/omnium-tilting-rack-bracket/\">Omnium Tilting Rack Bracket</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"f08b7a0ddc7ac4fd3a873c37a6d08f9a571dba7069439a95179c0ec44814ad15","category":"Cycling"}